## 0.1.2 (unreleased)

  - Default timeout to None. This allows the plugin to differentiate
    from a lack of a timeout given to a 0 timeout.
  - Ranges with more than two parts are invalid. [GH-1]

## 0.1.1 (August 1, 2011)

  - Default `host` to None
  - Default `timeout` to 0

## 0.1.0 (July 28, 2011)

  - Initial release
